---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="AI Security — Proprietary Threat Monitoring for Your Business — LeadFair"
  description="LeadFair runs its own AI security intelligence system — continuous threat monitoring, automated scanning, and encrypted data protection. Built for the AI era, not retrofitted."
  headline="Built for the AI Era. Secured Like It."
  subheadline="Most AI tools bolt security on as an afterthought. LeadFair runs proprietary security intelligence that monitors threats, scans for vulnerabilities, and keeps your data locked down — automatically."
  accentColor="primary"
>
  <!-- What We Protect Against -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-dots opacity-30"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-center mb-4">Security That Runs Itself</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16 text-lg">You shouldn't have to think about AI security. LeadFair handles it behind the scenes so you can focus on your business.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover card-glow-blue">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Continuous Threat Monitoring</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Our AI security agents scan the threat landscape daily — tracking new attack techniques, prompt injection methods, and AI-specific vulnerabilities before they can reach your business.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover card-glow-blue">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Automated Security Scanning</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Every piece of LeadFair's code is regularly scanned against the latest known threats — including AI-specific attacks that traditional security tools miss entirely.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover card-glow-blue">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-orange w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Encrypted Everything</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">All your data — business knowledge, call recordings, lead info, team conversations — is encrypted at rest and in transit. It never leaves LeadFair's infrastructure unprotected.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover card-glow-blue">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 18.364A9 9 0 005.636 5.636m12.728 12.728A9 9 0 015.636 5.636m12.728 12.728L5.636 5.636"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Never Sold. Never Shared.</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Your business data is yours. We don't sell it, we don't share it with partners, and we don't use it to train AI models for anyone else. Period.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover card-glow-blue">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Prompt Injection Protection</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">AI tools are vulnerable to prompt injection — where someone tricks the AI into doing something it shouldn't. LeadFair's security system specifically monitors and defends against these attacks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover card-glow-blue">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-orange w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Always Up to Date</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">The AI threat landscape changes weekly. Our security intelligence system updates automatically — you don't need to install patches, run updates, or think about it at all.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why This Matters -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-24 bg-gradient-blue-green">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid opacity-30"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-center mb-16">Why AI Security Is Different</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover">
          <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
            <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-12 h-12 rounded-xl shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Traditional Security Isn't Enough</h3>
              <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">Firewalls and antivirus were built for a different era. AI tools face new kinds of threats — prompt injection, data poisoning, model manipulation — that traditional security doesn't even look for. Most AI platforms rely entirely on their cloud provider's security and hope for the best.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover">
          <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
            <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-12 h-12 rounded-xl shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">LeadFair Runs Its Own Security Intelligence</h3>
              <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">We built a proprietary AI security agent that researches new threats, analyzes attack patterns, and scans our own systems — automatically. It's not a third-party add-on or a checkbox on a compliance form. It's a core part of how LeadFair operates.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover">
          <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
            <div class="icon-box icon-box-orange w-12 h-12 rounded-xl shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">You Get the Protection Without the Work</h3>
              <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">You don't need to understand prompt injection or AI attack vectors. You don't need to configure anything. LeadFair's security runs in the background — always on, always current, always protecting your business data and your customers' information.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Protect -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-24 bg-gradient-warm">
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-center mb-16">What's Protected</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 card-hover flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-10 h-10 rounded-lg shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-text font-medium">Your Company Companion knowledge — policies, procedures, pricing</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 card-hover flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-10 h-10 rounded-lg shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-text font-medium">Call recordings, transcripts, and AI receptionist conversations</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 card-hover flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-10 h-10 rounded-lg shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-text font-medium">Lead and customer data in your CRM pipeline</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 card-hover flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-10 h-10 rounded-lg shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-text font-medium">Team conversations, automations, and internal workflows</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
